Update to previous review, was explained that the low quality at high zoom is to conserve storage space for those with lower storage phones. My suggestion is to have two apps, a Lite version with an ad to support revenue rather than $1 price tag, and then a higher quality, larger sized, paid app. Also would love to see a Wiki app for quests and loot pools by the same developer. Definitely something I would pay for
replyContent: Zoom quality is compromise with taken storage space and working speed. Not all users has top smartphones or tablets. If you want to have a ultra high zoom level, that you should be prepared to download app that takes over 300mb space memory. In all cases, thank you for reply.
